=A {{ $json.strategy_type }} strategy for {{ $json.symbol }} futures was REJECTED.

Rejection reason: {{ $json.rejection_reason }}
Tier: {{ $json.last_tier }}
Metrics: Sharpe={{ $json.last_metrics.sharpe }}, MaxDD={{ $json.last_metrics.max_drawdown }}, Return={{ $json.last_metrics.total_return }}
Constraints: {{ $json.constraints }}

This is iteration {{ $json.iteration }} of {{ $json.max_iterations }}.

Analyze why this strategy failed and provide specific, actionable refinement suggestions. Focus on:
1. What parameters should change and in which direction
2. Whether the strategy logic itself needs restructuring
3. Risk management improvements

Output a concise refinement note (max 200 words) that will guide the next strategy generation attempt.

